  <div id="article-header">
    
    
      <h1 class="title">
      Convite: Processo aberto e colaborativo na criação do Novo Portal do Software Público Brasileiro
  </h1>
  <span class="publishing-info">
  <span class="date">
    februaro 19, 2013 0:00
  </span>
  <span class="author">
    , by Augusto Herrmann
  </span>
  <span class="comments">
     - <a href="/software-publico/blog/convite-processo-aberto-e-colaborativo-na-criacao-do-novo-portal-do-software-publico-brasileiro#comments_list"><span class='comment-count hide'>0</span><span class='comment-count-write-out'>no comments yet</span></a>
  </span>

<span class="followers-count">
|
    No one following this article yet.
</span>

</span>

